					<a class="addthis_button_linkedin" addthis:url="http://radar.oreilly.com/2014/01/lessons-learned-from-my-time-at-the-cfpb.html" addthis:title="Lessons learned from my time at the CFPB"></a>		

					<div class="clear"></div>

